# UI Components

The project uses a combination of custom UI components and components from Radix UI primitives.

## UI Component Library
- [components/ui/button.tsx](mdc:components/ui/button.tsx): Button component
- [components/ui/input.tsx](mdc:components/ui/input.tsx): Input component
- [components/ui/textarea.tsx](mdc:components/ui/textarea.tsx): Textarea component
- [components/ui/select.tsx](mdc:components/ui/select.tsx): Select component
- [components/ui/dialog.tsx](mdc:components/ui/dialog.tsx): Dialog component
- [components/ui/dropdown-menu.tsx](mdc:components/ui/dropdown-menu.tsx): Dropdown menu
- [components/ui/sidebar.tsx](mdc:components/ui/sidebar.tsx): Navigation sidebar
- [components/ui/card.tsx](mdc:components/ui/card.tsx): Card component

## UI Component Patterns
- Components are built using the shadcn approach
- Many components use Radix UI primitives for accessibility
- All components are styled with TailwindCSS
- Use composition patterns when building new components
